Title: Donal Skehan’s pre-festive feast to kick off the season
Description: By the time late November rolls around, most people have at least one foot in Christmas and the other still trying to get through the week. My wife, Sofie, always makes us hold off any decorations as long as possible, as our boys have birthdays on the November 27 and December 1, so we try and keep a little separation. This is the in-between season – dinner should feel like a nod to the season without the full three French hens.
URL: https://www.independent.ie/life/food-drink/recipes/donal-skehans-pre-festive-feast-to-kick-off-the-season/a930692521.html
